{"tid":1171842,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"龜縮喺電腦後既冚家鏟仇思達屌初一義士","createTime":"2019-05-26T04:06:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-11T12:42:45.000Z","uid":126283,"like":5,"dislike":25,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"68f74f710aacf8c6b89be5eb9941e277c0798dff","tid":1171842,"uid":126283,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-26T04:06:42.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/YicJJEDWq1M\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FYicJJEDWq1M&d=mZhSvp2BRS%2BtHw05K%2FyMFIL97yTsFD7TFgzLZRxFgWk%3D&h=030bde9a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/YicJJEDWq1M</a><br />\n<br />\n0:39 問題係想同真真正正去做，我成日講唔好得個「想」字，麻煩大家想移民既去創造經濟條件，<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">「想」呢就諗壞個腦，諗諗下愈諗愈激動走咗去掟磚啫只係會。</span></strong></span>呢啲事實嚟既。喂你諗左樣嘢諗唔開諗唔通，原來你係要搵錢先可以移民既，跟住你又搵唔到啦可能係，<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">咪愈諗愈激進囉，愈諗愈激進咪走去屌你老母走咗去泄憤囉其實係，你有啲友抗爭都唔係抗爭嚟架啦，唔該你面對現實喇，就泄憤咋嘛。你老母難道你走去燒個垃圾桶就係你可以推翻到特區政府咩，你泄憤咋嘛呢啲係。</span></span></strong>呢啲唔再講啦蹝時間。啫係你個人就係會咁架喇，<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">你愈來愈諗唔通諗唔開既時候就會愈諗愈激進成日要抗爭呢樣果樣。</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n15:12 喂我都唔係點你去死喇，<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">我冇叫你走去掟磚燒垃圾桶乜乜物物，果啲就真係冚家鏟嚟啦，</span></strong></span>果啲就令到你留有刑事案底走唔到。你信我喇<br />\n<br />\n一條片得罪哂本土派、義士、黃毓民、Barry Ma、有移民想法既人<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n尤其毓民真係陰功，為撐韓國瑜晚年失節都算、個鋼造春袋五癆七傷以為以後唔會有人再咬，而家又黎一個仇思達喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />睇路啦老人家<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"163f7894d67179af89fc10322b722c579d5d57fc","tid":1171842,"uid":126283,"like":12,"dislike":3,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-26T04:08:52.000Z","msg":"一撚定狙擊到你仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實大灣駒政治生涯已完(7)<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/LOyvtU\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/LOyvtU</a>"},{"pid":"ac66a504f6d8a4f2e7ee41b80b11a06d17672254","tid":1171842,"uid":126283,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-26T05:06:39.000Z","msg":"賤種仇思達仆街死喇去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c9e886f97ac19f55f7b8a11029fa29fc6ee43a2","tid":1171842,"uid":126283,"like":16,"dislike":1,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-26T07:57:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jwJfFtd.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjwJfFtd.png&h=b931db3d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nif you can't beat them, join them<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3965a44ee89fd25b39218ea34970f40057d2a65","tid":1171842,"uid":56326,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-26T07:58:20.000Z","msg":"衰撚過左膠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"552d3a774efd09da1703a6ded9efdc22888fe676","tid":1171842,"uid":126283,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-26T08:02:04.000Z","msg":"尋日屌堂主出黎「有事KFC無事周街痴」，仲重申自己2014冇撚出過黎，有咩ground攻擊人？"},{"pid":"bffa91bfd4d06439c8cde4b99ba9b24cd6e7baf9","tid":1171842,"uid":148987,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"b3965a44ee89fd25b39218ea34970f40057d2a65","tid":1171842,"uid":56326,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-26T